Name: Instant Death
About the game: Instant Death is a First-Person hardcore reflex game. Your goal is to complete the level without touching the color red. If you touch anything red you're DEAD. Also be careful and don't rush unless you're very confident in your skill since there are no checkpoints in the levels. If you die, you'll start from the beginning. 20 challenging and some almost impossible levels. No checkpoints. Techno Music. Pride of completing a level.
